<p>其中，<span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>ρ</mi><mi>μ</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\rho_\mu</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7167em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">ρ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">μ</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 是状态分布。</p>
<blockquote>
<p>证明略，且此定理适用于两个目标函数以及各种折扣情况</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>与随机策略的一个重要区别：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>梯度中<strong>不涉及动作 <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>A</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span></span></span></span> 的概率分布</strong>（为什么？因为是确定性的，没有概率分布）。</li>
<li>因此，确定性策略梯度方法<strong>天然是 off-policy 的</strong>。</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="算法描述-2" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#算法描述-2"><span>算法描述</span></a></h3>
